<view class="ga-page settings">
  <view class="ga-hero settings-hero">
    <text class="ga-hero__eyebrow">偏好</text>
    <view class="ga-hero__title">设置</view>
    <view class="ga-hero__desc">时区决定「今日」边界；位置与天气用于微调浇水节奏。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="ga-section-title">时区</view>
  <view class="settings-card ga-card">
    <view class="settings-field">
      <text class="settings-label">时区（影响「今日任务」按哪天算）</text>
      <picker mode="selector" range="{{labels}}" value="{{tzIndex}}" bindchange="onTzChange">
        <view class="settings-picker">{{labels[tzIndex]}}</view>
      </picker>
    </view>
    <view class="settings-primary" bindtap="onSave">保存时区</view>
  </view>

  <view class="ga-section-title">室内微气候</view>
  <view class="settings-card ga-card">
    <view class="settings-field settings-field--row">
      <text class="settings-label settings-label--inline">长期开空调（偏干）</text>
      <switch color="#2a4d3a" checked="{{airConditioning}}" bindchange="onAcChange" />
    </view>
    <view class="settings-field">
      <text class="settings-label">窗台 / 主采光朝向</text>
      <picker mode="selector" range="{{aspectLabels}}" value="{{aspectIndex}}" bindchange="onAspectChange">
        <view class="settings-picker">{{aspectLabels[aspectIndex]}}</view>
      </picker>
    </view>
    <view class="settings-primary settings-primary--secondary" bindtap="onSaveEnv">保存环境偏好</view>
    <text class="settings-hint-inline">与浇水间隔规则联动；保存后新建或「重算计划」的植物会采用最新偏好。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="ga-section-title">天气与环境</view>
  <view wx:if="{{needLocationTip}}" class="settings-callout ga-card">
    <text class="settings-callout__title">环境感知</text>
    <text class="settings-callout__body">保存当前位置后，会结合当地温湿度与短期预报微调浇水间隔。请在下方使用「使用当前定位」并允许授权。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="settings-card ga-card">
    <view wx:if="{{currentLive}}" class="settings-live">
      <view class="settings-live-icon settings-live-icon--{{liveWeatherKind}}"></view>
      <view class="settings-live-texts">
        <text class="settings-live-temp">{{currentLive.tempC}}°C</text>
        <text class="settings-live-sub">湿度 {{currentLive.rh}}%</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view wx:if="{{forecastDays.length}}" class="settings-chart">
      <text class="settings-chart-title">未来 3 日 · 气温示意</text>
      <view class="settings-chart-row">
        <block wx:for="{{forecastDays}}" wx:key="date">
          <view class="settings-chart-day">
            <view class="settings-live-icon settings-live-icon--sm settings-live-icon--{{item.weatherKind}}"></view>
            <text class="settings-chart-dm">{{item.dateShort}}</text>
            <view class="settings-chart-track">
              <view class="settings-chart-fill" style="height: {{item.barFillRpx}}rpx;"></view>
            </view>
            <text class="settings-chart-hilo">{{item.lo}}° / {{item.hi}}°</text>
          </view>
        </block>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="settings-field">
      <text class="settings-label">已保存位置（WGS84）</text>
      <text class="settings-mono">{{locSummary}}</text>
      <text wx:if="{{locationReadable}}" class="settings-location-label">{{locationReadable}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="settings-weather">{{weatherLine}}</view>
    <view wx:if="{{forecastHint}}" class="settings-hint">{{forecastHint}}</view>
    <view wx:if="{{forecastDays.length}}" class="settings-forecast-head">未来 3 天预报（按已保存时区）</view>
    <block wx:for="{{forecastDays}}" wx:key="date">
      <text class="settings-forecast-row">{{item.line}}</text>
    </block>
    <view class="settings-btns">
      <view class="settings-btn settings-btn--primary" bindtap="onPickLocation">使用当前定位</view>
      <view class="settings-btn settings-btn--ghost" bindtap="onClearLocation">清除位置</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="ga-section-title">第三方环境监测</view>
  <view class="settings-card ga-card">
    <text class="settings-hint-inline">硬件采用「设备直连云端 HTTPS」上报。配网（让设备拿到家里 Wi-Fi 密码）一次完成；之后所有读数自动入库并按植物展示在「植物 → 传感器与图表」中。</text>
    <view class="settings-primary settings-primary--secondary settings-mt" bindtap="onOpenProvision">前往配网向导</view>
    <text class="settings-hint-inline">完整架构与合规清单见工程文档：docs/engineering/miniprogram-third-party-sensors.md。</text>
  </view>
</view>
